@a84 34
<br>
that means:<br>
<br>
<span style="font-style: italic;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span
 style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-style: italic;">"...I like to run
an architecture independent operating-system
and
the 2nd reason is - I prefer outperforming RISC architecture more then
CISC."</span><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-style: italic;"></span><br>
<br>
or more concrete:<br>
<br>
<span style="font-style: italic;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span
 style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-style: italic;">"Linux is
OpenSource, </span><span
